stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Visible : polygon created at<br/>(drawHeading, drawTilt)

    note right of Visible
        polygon.getMap() === map
        edgeLabels.setMap(map)
        Area contributes to totalArea
        (unless excluded === true)
    end note

    note right of Hidden
        polygon.getMap() === null
        edgeLabels.setMap(null)
        Still in polygons[] and
        serializedPolygons,
        just not rendered.
    end note

    Visible --> Hidden : headingsMatch(drawHeading, currentHeading)<br/>=== false<br/>— OR —<br/>drawTilt !== currentTilt

    Hidden --> Visible : headingsMatch(drawHeading, currentHeading)<br/>=== true<br/>— AND —<br/>drawTilt === currentTilt

    note left of Hidden
        Checked by the effect in
        usePolygonDrawing whenever
        currentHeading or currentTilt
        changes (map 'idle' event).
    end note

    Visible --> [*] : deletePolygon(id)
    Hidden --> [*] : deletePolygon(id) / resetAll()
